Name: Number of Users
Description: Number of users to create and become primary users (ex: 0 or higher)

Name: Number of Computers
Description: Number of computers to create (ex: 0 or higher)

Name: Operating System Version List
Description: List of operating systems versions to use (separated by ;)

Name: Computer Name Prefix
Description: Computer name prefix to use when creating computers

Name: Computer VDI Prefix
Description: Computer name prefix for a VDI machine

Name: Computer Domain
Description: Domain to be assigned to new computers and also as fqdn

Name: Recent BIOS Release Date
Description: Recent BIOS release date to set

Name: Older BIOS Release Date
Description: Older BIOS release date to set. (at least 3 years old)

Name: Older BIOS Release Date Percentage
Description: Percentage of machines to set with date older than 3 years (ex: 0-100)
